   <a href=3D"https://www.nctm.org/archives/dr.math/faq/formulas/faq.pyrami=
d.html#pyramidfrustum">http://mathforum.org/dr.math/faq/formulas/faq.pyrami=
d.html</a>  =20

     V =3D h(B1 + B2 + sqrt[B1*B2])/3

